{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"他曾皱眉，而且转身离去，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"因为那个盲人来到他的面前。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"你怎能知道呢？他也许能受熏陶，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"或听忠告，而蒙教益。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"至于自满者，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你都逢迎他，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他不受熏陶，于你何干？"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"至于殷勤地来请教你，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"而且心怀敬畏者，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"你却怠慢他。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"绝不然！这确是一种教训。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"谁欲诵读它，就叫谁诵读它吧"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"它在珍贵的册页里；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"那些册页，是被称扬的，是被涤净的，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"是在许多书记的手里的；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"那些书记，是尊贵的，是善良的。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"该死的人！他是何等的忘恩！"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"安拉曾用什么创造他的呢？"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"是用精液。他曾创造他，并预定他发育的程序。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"然后，他使他的道路平易。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"然后，他使他死，并安葬他。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"然后，当他意欲的时候，他使他复活。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"绝不然，他还没有奉行他所命令他的事务。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"教人观察自己的食物吧！"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"我将雨水大量地倾注下来。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"然后，我使地面奇异地裂开，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"我在大地上生产百谷，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"与葡萄和苜蓿，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"与橄榄和海枣，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"与茂密的园圃，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"水果和牧草，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"以供你们和你们的牲畜享受。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"当震耳欲聋的轰声来临的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"在那日，各人将逃避自己的弟兄、"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"自己的父母、"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"自己的妻子儿女；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"在那日，各人将自顾不暇；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"在那日，许多面目是光华的，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"是喜笑的，是愉快的；"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"在那日，许多面目上，将有灰尘，"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"黧黑将蒙蔽它。"},{"SurahNumber":80,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"这等人，是不信道的，是荒淫的。"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当太阳黯黜的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"当星宿零落的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"当山峦崩溃的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"当孕驼被抛弃的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"当野兽被集合的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"当海洋澎湃的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"当灵魂被配合的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"当被活埋的女孩被询问的时候："},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"她为什么罪过而遭杀害呢？"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"当功过薄被展开的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"当天皮被揭去的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"当火狱被燃着的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"当乐园被送近的时候，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"每个人都知道他所作过的善恶。"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"我誓以运行的众星"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"没落的行星，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"和逝去时的黑夜，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"照耀时的早晨，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"这确是一个尊贵的使者的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他在宝座的主那里，是有权力的，是有地位的，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"是众望所归，而且忠於职守的。"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你们的朋友，不是一个疯人，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"他确已看见那个天使在明显的天边，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"他对幽玄不是吝教的。"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"这不是被放逐的恶魔的言辞，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"你们将往哪里去呢？"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"这只是对于众世界的教诲——"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"对於你们中欲循规蹈矩者的教诲，"},{"SurahNumber":81,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"你们不欲循规蹈矩，除非安拉——众世界的主——意欲的时候。"}]}